        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You leap from the shadows to strike at your foes. Stride up to your Speed, then Strike twice. If you were hidden or unnoticed by the target of these Strikes, the target is off-guard against both attacks. Your multiple attack penalty applies normally for both attacks.",
